{
  "stem": "8191.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In France in that time, you couldn't a diploma.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You had to have practical work for one year.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And knowing German, and it was a brand new Siemens, was a brand new in France.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was a-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a frozen situation between 1919 till 1930 between France and Germany.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But finally they broke the ice, and Siemens established the first.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there I was hired by Siemens without knowing that they want me to go to Germany.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I spent in Paris for two or three months with them, and then they say if I'd like to go.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they sent-- and so I went to Tempelhof.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I spent there-- and I fell into the medical division.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] And in that time, we worked on sound equipment.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And today, you have sound equipment that there's 10 million vibrations in a second.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And in that time, the vibration was only 200-- between 200 and 300 vibration in a second.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that's how I fell into sound.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I had-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I had a gift in me without going to school for vision in touch.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I used to-- I hear-- until today I hear music by touching [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] vibrations.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] So-- then between that time, I find a job.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I came back to Paris.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I had already diploma and I find a job with the company that was called, in that time, the Materiel Telephonique.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They owned the telephone company.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But that was really owned by Western Electric.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So I was with them maybe two or three months.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
